entries.femaleVariant: Lucy?
Lucy?
Lucy? What're you doin' here?
Why are you here?
This place needs two ripperdocs?
Could be workin' well outside of town already. Place already has a ripper.
How'd you wind up here?
Quiet. And it's Mia, not Lucy, got it?
It's not easy, but at least it feels like what I'm doing has purpose. Say... got a request.
Quiet. Mia – not Lucy. Got it? Now scram.
Uh-huh. But sheesh, that cover...  Oughta leave the city, y'know.
My brother left. Me, I'm needed more here.
Who, Octavio? Good guy, but hasn't learned all the ropes yet.
Yeah?
Regina pointed me to El Capitán, who then set me up with Octavio. I needed a place to lie low, and him – a professional.
Besides, we need all hands ready and available. If it's not infectious disease, it's drug-resistant fungal infections.
Think you'll get by all right here?
Listen, everyone—regardless of circumstance—has a right to get help, to live another day. Got that?
We're short on eddies and the kiddos need vaccinated. If ya can, toss something Octavio's way.
Lemme think on it.
Thanks.
Maelstrom's looking for you.
This cover's not gonna cut it, and Maelstrom's still after you. You gotta ditch the city.
I get it, don't wanna see my face. Leave you to it, then.
Are you still talking? Octavio!
Yeah?
This one over here, no aid for her, understood?
entries.maleVariant: This one over here, no aid for him, understood?

entries.femaleVariant: Whatever you say.
Leave you to it.
